OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FScattered
OL,6,Fshowers will clear during the evening
OL,7,Fleaving dry conditions and clear
OL,8,Fspells for a time overnight. Becoming
OL,9,Fcloudy by morning with patchy light
OL,10,Frain arriving.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA mostly cloudy day with
OL,13,Fsome patchy light rain, mainly in the
OL,14,Fafternoon. Drier at first with a
OL,15,Flittle brightness.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
