OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA dry
OL,6,Fstart to Sunday then outbreaks of
OL,7,Fheavy rain spread east. This followed
OL,8,Fby bright or sunny spells and showers,
OL,9,Fsome heavy, through the rest of the
OL,10,Fperiod.
